  "title": "Beauty Sales Consultant / Therapist",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Contribute to clinic sales through the promotion of clinic treatments to clients.</li>\n  <li>Assist in aesthetics procedures.</li>\n  <li>Handle all pre/post procedures care, registration, and counselling.</li>\n  <li>Prepare all the necessary equipment, tools, and consumables required in medical aesthetic procedures.</li>\n  <li>Serve clientele in all aspects of treatments.</li>\n  <li>Maintain order of patient cards and manage patient entries in POS.</li>\n  <li>Recommend appropriate aesthetic treatments to patients.</li>\n  <li>Assist in cashiering, inventory, ordering, &amp; database management.</li>\n  <li>Assist in maintaining quality service standards.</li>\n  <li>Ad hoc duties assigned by your supervisor(s).</li>\n</ul>",
